sendActionListMessage(TopicConnection, InitialContext, String, ComplexEventRuleActionListDocument, boolean) - Method in class it.cnr.isti.labse.glimpse.consumer.GlimpseAbstractConsumer
 
sendActionListMessage(TopicConnection, InitialContext, String, ComplexEventRuleActionListDocument, boolean) - Method in interface it.cnr.isti.labse.glimpse.consumer.GlimpseConsumer
Send a ActionList of rules to the monitoring infrastructure requesting an evaluation.
If the request is accepted, the monitoring will answer with a responseChannel where to connect
The actionList parameter is a list of action to provide to the Monitoring
To create it, you can use ComplexEventRuleActionListDocument class.
